	(262,NULL,28,2,'Triple Bill','triple_bill','Moving, elegant, inspiring and loving; an evening of dance and music that stays true to its traditional classica','<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; font-family: \'Lucida Sans\', Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16.799999237060547px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Moving, elegant, inspiring and loving; an evening of dance and music that stays true to its traditional classical roots through an extraordinary range of creations.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; font-family: \'Lucida Sans\', Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16.799999237060547px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">3rd Stage Dance Company return to Tobacco Factory Theatres after their sell out performance&nbsp;<em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Piano Moves</em>. This triple bill starts with an elegant and beautiful creation &ndash;&nbsp;<em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">JustWORDS</em>&nbsp;&ndash; a study of words and their meaning from a single short message to an interpretation of an entire story.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; font-family: \'Lucida Sans\', Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16.799999237060547px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">The second part&nbsp;<em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Invitation Only</em>&nbsp;shows work by invited choreographers Steve Johnstone (Off The Map Dance Company) and Kerry Biggin (Principal Dancer and Rehearsal Director of Matthew Bourne&rsquo;s New Adventures) and welcomes to the stage a performance by RISE, one of Bristol&rsquo;s leading youth dance companies.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; font-family: \'Lucida Sans\', Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16.799999237060547px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">The third and final part of the evening,&nbsp;<em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Never Brought to Mind</em>, is accompanied by live music from The Ryan O&rsquo;Reilly Band giving a feature evening of their tour. With harmonies that find their way through every bone in your body and sound so sweet it nurtures your soul, they give stories and identities for the people in the street.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; font-family: \'Lucida Sans\', Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16.799999237060547px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">3rd Stage Dance Company create opportunities for dancers to return to dance after time away. It brings desire and passion to the stage through classical contemporary dance that is accessible and enjoyable for all ages.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; font-family: \'Lucida Sans\', Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16.799999237060547px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&ldquo;3rd Stage Dance Company seems to have an incredibly solid and morally grounded ethos which makes it very unique&hellip;as an audience member it was a very inspiring performance&rdquo;</strong>&nbsp;Richard Chappell, Choreographer</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; font-family: \'Lucida Sans\', Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16.799999237060547px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Click&nbsp;<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-color: #990033; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #666666; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;\" title=\"here\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JYj6Xd6JG7A\">here</a>&nbsp;to see the company in rehearsal</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; font-family: \'Lucida Sans\', Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16.799999237060547px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Running time</strong>&nbsp;approx. 2hrs 30mins (inc. two intervals)</p>','','BS4 3EN','51.4426688','-2.5683698999999933',NULL,NULL,1,0,1,0,NULL,NULL,'2014-07-01 00:00:01','2014-07-01 00:00:01','2014-07-14 10:25:25',0),
